title: 833. Rookies & Second-Year Players to Buy in the AFC & NFC North
itunes:title: 833. Rookies & Second-Year Players to Buy in the AFC & NFC North
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys each give a rookie and second-year player they'd buy from the AFC North teams. Then for the rest of the show, the duo each give a rookie and second-year player they'd buy from the NFC North teams.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
